data.description: Attention Buyers looking for space and privacy! Welcome home to this delightful Brooklyn Park rambler. Updates throughout include new floors, updated kitchen, oversized two car garage, a complete wood privacy fence, raised garden beds, and a sweet pergola oasis for backyard cookouts and campfires.  A separate 200sq ft shed has a conduit from the garage ready for electric as well as a loft for additional storage.
